<style>
	.crowd-wrapper{ background-color:white; border: 1px rgb(188, 188, 188) solid; border-radius: 15px;width: 1120px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto; padding-bottom: 50px;}
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container { width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; overflow: hidden; font-size: 16px; font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", "微软雅黑"; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container a, .crowd-wrapper .question-container a:hover { color: #6d6d6d; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .question { text-align: center; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 40px; margin-top: 30px; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .answer img { margin-top: 10px; max-width: 1000px; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .answer .fu { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .answer .red { color: #E53333; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .answer ol li { margin-bottom: 25px; }
	.crowd-wrapper .question-container .answer ol li .pay-step { margin-bottom: 15px; }
</style>
<div class="crowd-wrapper">
<div class="question-container">
    <div class="question">
        外籍人士如何完成京东众筹支付
    </div>
    <div class="answer">
        <p>云棒在京东众筹以来，有很多人外籍人士想购买云棒但遇到支付困难，特说明如下：</p>
        <ol>
            <li>外籍人士因身份问题无法进行京东快捷支付，只能通过网银来支付<span class="red">(网银支付仅支持电脑客户端)。</span></li>
            <li>
                网银支付流程说明如下：（以下截图说明以工商银行为例子）<br /><br />
                <div class="pay-step">
                    第一步：在“<span class="red">订单信息确认页</span>”点击“<span class="red">立即付款</span>”<br/>
                    <img src="http://www.meibeike.com/views/default/skin/default/images_2/20160225160225_45397.png" alt=""/>
                </div>
                <div class="pay-step">
                    第二步：选择“<span class="red">网银支付</span>”<br/>
                    <img src="http://www.meibeike.com/views/default/skin/default/images_2/20160225160239_75479.png" alt=""/>
                </div>
                <div class="pay-step">
                    第三步：以工商银行为例，选择存储卡并确认跳转网银并支付。（要确保你的网银每日的单笔限额超过3万）<br/>
                    <img src="http://www.meibeike.com/views/default/skin/default/images_2/20160225160303_83974.png" alt=""/>
                </div>
                <div class="pay-step">
                    第四步：选择“<span class="red">其他支付方式（网银支付）</span>”并且输入<span class="red">卡（账）号</span>，点击下一步即可<br/>
                    <img src="http://www.meibeike.com/views/default/skin/default/images_2/20160225160317_54771.png" alt=""/>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <div class="fu">
            附: 以下是各银行网银支付的支付限额<br />
            <img src="http://www.meibeike.com/views/default/skin/default/images_2/20160225160126_22388.png" alt=""/>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>